summary: An email exchange between FBI personnel regarding the need for assistance to execute a search warrant at Jeffrey Epstein's Manhattan residence for digital media and computer equipment on July 11, 2019. Most of the C20 team is in Florida interviewing victims.

persons.name: SSAI

events.title: Planned Search of Epstein's Manhattan Residence
events.description: C20 (likely an FBI team) planned to execute a search warrant at Jeffrey Epstein's residence in Manhattan for digital media and computer equipment.

keyFacts: The FBI's C20 team planned to execute a search warrant at Jeffrey Epstein's Manhattan residence on July 11, 2019.
The primary objective of the search was to seize digital media and computer equipment.
Most of the C20 team was in Florida at the time, conducting victim interviews.
The email exchange demonstrates active, multi-state investigation efforts by the FBI in July 2019.
